## 📚 Citation

If you use AoS in academic work, please cite:

> Schreiner, J. (2026). *Algorithm of Sustainability: A Guide to a Fair and Stable Economy for the 21st Century.*

(Full citation details available in [`/references/Bibliography.md`](references/Bibliography.md).)

---

## 🤝 Contributing

Researchers are invited to contribute by:

- Submitting theoretical extensions  
- Providing simulation models  
- Conducting empirical evaluations  
- Proposing mathematical refinements  
- Submitting peer‑review comments  

Please use **pull requests** or open an **issue** for discussion.

